A workflow from downloading an ERA5 pres-level data file to GRIST-readable atmosphere initial.

(1) go to download for getting ERA5 data
(2) go to scripts for steps 1-3
(3) go to data and do step4 for final input.

ERA5: "WARNING 2021-06-25: Variable "Orography" is now named "Geopotential". No change in the data themselves.   
Previous API requests asking for "Orography" will fail now. To download the corresponding data the API request should ask for "Geopotential".
